summary: This is an FBI 302 form documenting an interview conducted on July 27, 2020, at a residence in Maricopa, Arizona. The interviewee was provided with a copy of a related police report on August 4, 2020. The document is part of an investigation file and contains no recommendations or conclusions.

events.title: FBI Interview at Residence
events.description: An individual was interviewed at their residence in Maricopa, Arizona, by FBI Special Agents and a Police Department officer.

events.title: Provision of Police Report
events.description: The interviewee was provided with a copy of the City of Police Department Officer Report summarizing the July 27, 2020 interview.

keyFacts: An FBI interview was conducted on July 27, 2020, at a residence in Maricopa, Arizona.
The interviewee was provided with a copy of the related police report on August 4, 2020.
The document is an FBI 302 form, which is a record of an interview, and it explicitly states it contains no recommendations or conclusions.
All personal identifying information (name, DOB, phone number) of the interviewee is redacted in the provided text.
The document is part of investigation file number SOD-NY-3027571.
